query:
SELECT 
  id,
  customerId,
  amount,
  balanceBefore,
  balanceAfter,
  description,
  createdAt
FROM balance_transactions
WHERE customerId = 480001 AND amount = 120
ORDER BY createdAt DESC
LIMIT 5
